CatDescriptText: A portion of the poster reads: "Young Adult Chapter of NAACP Presents the First Annual Pastel Ball Hotel Webster Hall (Oakland) Sat. 9 p.m. until ? - July 14, 1962....In Person...Bill [D]ogg[ett]."
TitMainTitle: Three men, one possibly Bill Doggett, and two women seated at a table in Loendi Club with musical notes on the wall, and two men holding posters advertising Bill Doggett performance
